WEBVTT

00:00:01.199 --> 00:00:06.640
I'm on late tonight; it's 10:00. I know

00:00:04.560 --> 00:00:08.800
I usually come on at 9:00. My

00:00:06.640 --> 00:00:10.800
friend Billy Burke called, and I was so

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:12.639
excited. I'll never

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:14.719
say I've got to get off the phone to do a

00:00:12.639 --> 00:00:17.119
broadcast when he calls, because I'm telling

00:00:14.719 --> 00:00:19.680
you, it's a stream of living water

00:00:17.119 --> 00:00:21.198
coming out of that man. What a

00:00:19.680 --> 00:00:23.680
blessing. I got to talk to him for over

00:00:21.199 --> 00:00:26.000
two hours tonight, and I

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:28.640
cherish those times

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:31.039
listening to the old stories of

00:00:28.640 --> 00:00:32.800
the generals he's had the

00:00:31.039 --> 00:00:35.280
pleasure to walk in the

00:00:32.800 --> 00:00:37.839
shadows of and the people

00:00:35.280 --> 00:00:40.719
he's been able to be around in ministry, like Kathryn Kuhlman

00:00:37.840 --> 00:00:42.480
and Ralph Wilkerson—all

00:00:40.719 --> 00:00:45.760
these great people. It's

00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:48.640
amazing. I just go, 'Golly.'You

00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:49.839
know, I lose track of time. When

00:00:48.640 --> 00:00:50.960
you're talking to somebody like that and

00:00:49.840 --> 00:00:52.559
you're listening about the old

00:00:50.960 --> 00:00:55.760
people, you lose track of time and you

00:00:52.559 --> 00:00:57.360
go, 'My God, what an honor that you

00:00:55.760 --> 00:00:59.680
would call and talk to me when the Lord

00:00:57.360 --> 00:01:01.840
tells him to,'you know, just to

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:04.479
encourage me to keep going. He listens

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:05.920
to us and prays with us, and it's a

00:01:04.479 --> 00:01:07.360
blessing that he would pray with us. I

00:01:05.920 --> 00:01:10.320
have so many amazing people that come

00:01:07.360 --> 00:01:12.560
and pray—so many amazing men and

00:01:10.320 --> 00:01:13.919
women of God, big platforms, little

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:15.760
platforms, all kinds of people all

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:18.000
around the world that come and watch us

00:01:15.760 --> 00:01:21.439
and pray with us. I mean,

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:23.200
what an honor. You know,

00:01:21.439 --> 00:01:24.960
God has called us, I guess, for such a

00:01:23.200 --> 00:01:27.680
time as this right now to do

00:01:24.960 --> 00:01:30.240
what we're doing, and I'm humbled by

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:31.759
what the Lord has done. It's

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:38.199
amazing.

00:01:31.759 --> 00:01:38.200
But I want to go—how many are here?

00:01:39.759 --> 00:01:45.439
Oh, we have more than enough. All right,

00:01:41.840 --> 00:01:47.759
1,900 right now. We'll start.

00:01:45.439 --> 00:01:49.679
Well, good evening everybody. Thank you

00:01:47.759 --> 00:01:51.439
for joining me. We're going to go over

00:01:49.680 --> 00:01:53.280
some of the news and what's going on

00:01:51.439 --> 00:01:55.119
today with the signs of the

00:01:53.280 --> 00:01:57.520
times and the coming of the Lord Jesus

00:01:55.119 --> 00:02:00.560
Christ. It's all around us. I'm telling

00:01:57.520 --> 00:02:02.960
you, Jesus Christ is coming, and I hope

00:02:00.560 --> 00:02:04.880
you have your anticipation out there.

00:02:02.960 --> 00:02:07.119
You know, it's like I

00:02:04.880 --> 00:02:09.038
said, talking to my friend. He said, 'So

00:02:07.119 --> 00:02:11.520
many people have said that for so

00:02:09.038 --> 00:02:13.760
long, so many years, all the time.

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:15.920
We've heard that.'But I asked him,

00:02:13.760 --> 00:02:18.399
'Sir, do you believe Jesus is

00:02:15.920 --> 00:02:20.079
coming soon?'And he said, 'Brandon, I

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:22.959
believe he could come back tomorrow.'That's

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:26.319
as you watch the news, as you

00:02:22.959 --> 00:02:29.120
see the things happening

00:02:26.319 --> 00:02:31.200
all around us, you have an anticipation.

00:02:29.120 --> 00:02:32.720
And even he was saying, 'I'm

00:02:31.200 --> 00:02:34.160
surprised he hadn't already come.'When

00:02:32.720 --> 00:02:36.080
you look at what's going on in the news,

00:02:34.160 --> 00:02:37.280
I

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:38.480
believe he could come back tomorrow. I

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:40.959
believe he could come back this week.

00:02:38.480 --> 00:02:42.959
That's how soon I feel like

00:02:40.959 --> 00:02:46.800
it's coming. You can feel

00:02:42.959 --> 00:02:49.120
it inside, and it's cool to see it.

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:52.080
As you see what happened today, as you

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:54.480
see what's going on with America today,

00:02:54.480 --> 00:02:58.720
talking to him about the

00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:00.879
revival and talking to Billy about what

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:03.200
he believes is coming—it's

00:03:00.879 --> 00:03:06.239
amazing

00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:07.679
to hear him talk because you know

00:03:06.239 --> 00:03:10.239
the Holy Spirit's going to lead

00:03:07.680 --> 00:03:12.720
us all in the same direction, just

00:03:10.239 --> 00:03:14.879
differently: different frames, different

00:03:12.720 --> 00:03:17.359
pictures, but we all get the

00:03:14.879 --> 00:03:19.920
same puzzle piece, right?

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:22.560
Talking about the portals and

00:03:19.920 --> 00:03:24.640
the revival, I would love for him to

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:26.159
come on if he ever feels

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:29.518
comfortable. I don't ever try to push

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:31.920
things, but to talk about what

00:03:29.519 --> 00:03:34.159
he's seen about the healing miracles in

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:36.958
his ministry with Kathryn Kuhlman and

00:03:34.159 --> 00:03:39.440
being

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:41.519
around and seeing eyes open and ears

00:03:39.440 --> 00:03:43.680
open in his own ministry and flowing

00:03:41.519 --> 00:03:45.920
with the gift of the Spirit like he has.

00:03:43.680 --> 00:03:47.840
One day, I believe he will. But

00:03:45.920 --> 00:03:49.040
I'm so excited because he wants

00:03:47.840 --> 00:03:50.480
to do a meeting. He's always talking

00:03:49.040 --> 00:03:52.239
about doing meetings and

00:03:50.480 --> 00:03:54.319
what the Lord is doing for this

00:03:52.239 --> 00:03:58.799
season of his life. You know, he's going into

00:03:54.319 --> 00:04:02.079
his 70s now, and this

00:03:58.799 --> 00:04:03.680
chapter where he's at, being an elder

00:04:02.080 --> 00:04:06.080
flowing in the gifts of the Spirit and

00:04:03.680 --> 00:04:07.519
where God has called him, it's amazing. Because

00:04:06.080 --> 00:04:09.040
I'm new and I'm just

00:04:07.519 --> 00:04:10.720
starting out, listening

00:04:09.040 --> 00:04:12.560
to somebody who's been in it for 50-some

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:14.560
years, for us who are just

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:16.160
cutting our teeth, we don't even know. I

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:17.759
feel like I'm just trying to

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:20.639
find my bearings and going where

00:04:17.759 --> 00:04:24.080
God has me. It's amazing

00:04:20.639 --> 00:04:25.759
to

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:27.840
hear about healings. I love to hear

00:04:25.759 --> 00:04:30.479
the testimonies of what Jesus has

00:04:27.840 --> 00:04:33.758
done for so many people. People

00:04:30.479 --> 00:04:36.800
think, 'Is healing still for today?'Yes, healing is for today.

00:04:33.759 --> 00:04:38.720
The delivering

00:04:36.800 --> 00:04:40.800
power of the Holy Spirit is still for

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:43.280
today. He is the same yesterday, today,

00:04:40.800 --> 00:04:45.360
and forever. And what he did 2,000 years

00:04:43.280 --> 00:04:48.000
ago, he's still doing today. If you believe—I

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:49.280
believe with all my heart—we're

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:51.199
going to see some of the

00:04:49.280 --> 00:04:54.559
greatest miracles that we've ever seen

00:04:51.199 --> 00:04:56.160
before in the days ahead.

00:04:54.560 --> 00:04:58.240
I would say,

00:04:58.240 --> 00:05:01.520
'Do you

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:03.840
believe the revival will be all over America?'and

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:05.599
he said, 'I believe it will be

00:05:03.840 --> 00:05:07.440
in

00:05:05.600 --> 00:05:09.520
pockets.'There'll

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:12.080
be portals; that's exactly what

00:05:09.520 --> 00:05:15.840
I've seen. That's why I keep telling

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:17.520
you I see a migration. There are

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:19.119
so many people that will be

00:05:17.520 --> 00:05:21.599
moving. Yeah, the Holy Spirit

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:23.680
will be moving in areas, but there'll be

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:26.080
some places that are greater than

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:28.240
others. I have brought up Church of

00:05:26.080 --> 00:05:30.639
His Presence.

00:05:28.240 --> 00:05:33.280
John Kilpatrick—why I keep bringing up

00:05:30.639 --> 00:05:35.120
this man. I don't know this man, but I

00:05:33.280 --> 00:05:37.758
know him by the spirit of what I know in

00:05:35.120 --> 00:05:41.759
my spirit. When I pray for Church of His

00:05:37.759 --> 00:05:44.800
Presence, the Lord said that he did it

00:05:41.759 --> 00:05:47.600
once in his ministry and the well is not

00:05:44.800 --> 00:05:51.360
there like it was, but it's coming

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:54.160
back in a greater capacity. And he said,

00:05:51.360 --> 00:05:56.240
'I'm renewing John Kilpatrick's

00:05:54.160 --> 00:05:58.560
health like youth is renewed like

00:05:56.240 --> 00:06:00.320
the eagles, and he will finish strong.

00:05:58.560 --> 00:06:02.000
It's not time for him to go home

00:06:00.320 --> 00:06:03.759
yet.'He

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:05.440
will be a person—I saw him

00:06:03.759 --> 00:06:06.800
sitting on the stage and the glory and

00:06:05.440 --> 00:06:09.039
the presence of the Lord filling Church

00:06:06.800 --> 00:06:12.880
of His Presence again. Then I saw

00:06:09.039 --> 00:06:15.120
places like a church in

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:16.800
Minnesota. I saw a major move of God in

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:19.280
a church in Minnesota. I saw

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:22.319
Collinsville, where Pastor Chip

00:06:19.280 --> 00:06:25.520
and Candace are, and Branson.

00:06:22.319 --> 00:06:27.280
I saw I-35,

00:06:25.520 --> 00:06:30.400
Oklahoma City going down to Dallas-Fort

00:06:27.280 --> 00:06:33.758
Worth, a major move of God coming

00:06:30.400 --> 00:06:36.159
on the highway, I-35. I've seen it out in the

00:06:33.759 --> 00:06:38.800
Crescent, Oklahoma area. I've

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:40.400
seen it in

00:06:38.800 --> 00:06:43.520
places that you would least

00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:46.560
expect it, but it's because of the

00:06:43.520 --> 00:06:49.039
cultivation of prayer. Much prayer

00:06:46.560 --> 00:06:51.840
has gone up in these areas. It will come

00:06:49.039 --> 00:06:53.759
out of prayer; it's bathed in prayer.

00:06:51.840 --> 00:06:57.359
The one that I've seen in the Mabee

00:06:53.759 --> 00:06:59.360
Center with ORU and with the

00:06:57.360 --> 00:07:03.199
Victory over across the street with Paul Daugherty

00:06:59.360 --> 00:07:05.840
being the overflow—a major revival

00:07:03.199 --> 00:07:08.160
coming to Tulsa, Oklahoma.

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:11.359
I believe that Tulsa is a hot spot for

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:14.720
the end-time move. I believe there'll

00:07:11.360 --> 00:07:16.720
be areas that are stronger than others.

00:07:14.720 --> 00:07:19.199
And even as I talked to my friend

00:07:16.720 --> 00:07:21.680
today, he said, 'Brandon, I believe that

00:07:19.199 --> 00:07:24.400
it won't be like that everywhere

00:07:21.680 --> 00:07:26.080
because not everybody wants it. Not

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:28.159
everybody wants to cultivate His

00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:30.960
presence. Nobody wants to pay the price

00:07:28.160 --> 00:07:33.759
in prayer. Not everybody wants that. But

00:07:30.960 --> 00:07:36.318
there's a remnant of people

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:38.800
that are hungry, that are desperate for

00:07:36.319 --> 00:07:41.039
a move of God in these last days, and

00:07:38.800 --> 00:07:42.639
you're about to see one of the greatest harvests

00:07:41.039 --> 00:07:44.639
of souls this world has ever

00:07:42.639 --> 00:07:47.280
seen before.'But I saw people

00:07:44.639 --> 00:07:49.599
migrating, and I saw properties in

00:07:47.280 --> 00:07:52.719
Tulsa, properties in areas where it

00:07:49.599 --> 00:07:54.639
will be so hard to even find rent houses

00:07:52.720 --> 00:07:57.440
because of the fact that people are just

00:07:54.639 --> 00:07:59.199
trying to get around the revival.

00:07:57.440 --> 00:08:01.440
Will it last a long time? I don't

00:07:59.199 --> 00:08:04.479
believe it will; I believe it'll be a

00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:06.400
quick work. But I saw a major move of

00:08:04.479 --> 00:08:08.800
God in Brazil and all these other areas.

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:10.960
And I keep talking about it—a new Azusa

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:14.080
Street for Asia coming out of South

00:08:10.960 --> 00:08:16.159
Korea. Just talking that over. What was

00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:20.318
it like in the tent revival? What was it

00:08:16.160 --> 00:08:22.639
like reading books

00:08:20.319 --> 00:08:24.720
from Kathryn Kuhlman and Oral Roberts

00:08:22.639 --> 00:08:26.560
and A.A. Allen and all these that walked

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:30.280
before? Diana has been on a

00:08:26.560 --> 00:08:30.280
scavenger hunt lately

00:08:31.120 --> 00:08:36.159
going through the books. I think she's

00:08:33.839 --> 00:08:38.159
gotten probably ten new books in the

00:08:36.159 --> 00:08:40.240
last week. These are old books that

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:43.519
are hardly printed anymore, that you

00:08:40.240 --> 00:08:45.519
can't find,

00:08:43.519 --> 00:08:48.880
and she finds them in certain

00:08:45.519 --> 00:08:50.080
places, looking for them to try to

00:08:48.880 --> 00:08:52.640
find books that are not in print

00:08:50.080 --> 00:08:53.760
anymore. Like, where are the books not in

00:08:52.640 --> 00:08:55.760
print? What did

00:08:53.760 --> 00:08:58.800
they read? How did they get

00:08:55.760 --> 00:09:00.399
where they got? I told her,

00:08:58.800 --> 00:09:02.000
"I love your brain, the way you

00:09:00.399 --> 00:09:04.720
think, baby."She's asking,

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:06.560
"How did they get it? How was Kathryn Kuhlman

00:09:04.720 --> 00:09:09.360
inspired? What

00:09:06.560 --> 00:09:11.518
inspired her? What books did she read?

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:13.920
What inspired Oral Roberts to keep

00:09:11.519 --> 00:09:16.720
going? Where was he at when he

00:09:13.920 --> 00:09:18.800
first started, like us? What inspired

00:09:16.720 --> 00:09:21.519
them to keep going? What fed their flame?"Yeah,

00:09:18.800 --> 00:09:23.120
the Bible. But there were

00:09:21.519 --> 00:09:25.360
people that you listen to and you glean

00:09:23.120 --> 00:09:28.000
from, like I do, Billy. And you listen to

00:09:25.360 --> 00:09:31.120
them and you go, "Okay,

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:33.200
I get it."Why try to

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:35.200
learn it yourself and reinvent the wheel

00:09:33.200 --> 00:09:38.880
whenever somebody's already walked in it

00:09:35.200 --> 00:09:40.880
and they can tell you, "That doesn't work.

00:09:38.880 --> 00:09:43.920
That didn't work for

00:09:40.880 --> 00:09:45.920
me,"versus

00:09:43.920 --> 00:09:47.360
the people who keep doing

00:09:45.920 --> 00:09:48.800
something and hit the wall?

00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:50.560
You learn out of

00:09:48.800 --> 00:09:52.959
being dumb and you go, "Well, that really hurt."You

00:09:50.560 --> 00:09:54.479
know, the car door

00:09:52.959 --> 00:09:56.479
hurts when you slam your hand in it.

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:58.160
Don't do that; that's dumb. Versus

00:09:56.480 --> 00:10:01.351
the one that says, "I've already done that;

00:09:58.160 --> 00:10:01.351
don't do that."So,

00:10:02.240 --> 00:10:05.920
I don't know. I try to be

00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:07.199
encouraging to you all, but that's

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:08.560
where I was tonight. That's

00:10:08.560 --> 00:10:14.800
why I'm late. But praise the Lord.

00:10:11.440 --> 00:10:18.320
I

00:10:14.800 --> 00:10:22.079
want to show you some of the things that

00:10:18.320 --> 00:10:25.120
happened today in the news. The

00:10:22.079 --> 00:10:26.959
earthquakes are taking place. And then

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:28.640
what we saw last night about the

00:10:26.959 --> 00:10:30.640
metamorphosis,

00:10:28.640 --> 00:10:32.560
and the Lord showed us we're about to

00:10:30.640 --> 00:10:35.439
see something we've never seen before.

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:37.599
We're about to see a butterfly fly out

00:10:35.440 --> 00:10:40.240
of the church that we've never seen

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:43.200
before. I saw colors on a butterfly, a

00:10:40.240 --> 00:10:46.800
beautiful

00:10:43.200 --> 00:10:50.480
mosaic that was

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:53.040
so beautiful and so vibrant. And as I

00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:55.920
was looking through this cocoon, this

00:10:53.040 --> 00:10:57.920
caterpillar was inside,

00:10:55.920 --> 00:11:00.319
pushing with all its might.

00:10:57.920 --> 00:11:02.240
It represented the church,

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:04.560
the body of Christ pushing

00:11:02.240 --> 00:11:07.120
with all its might. And I saw a breaking

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:09.839
point of this caterpillar coming out of

00:11:07.120 --> 00:11:11.680
the cocoon as a beautiful new butterfly.

00:11:09.839 --> 00:11:13.760
And the Lord said, "Do you see that

00:11:11.680 --> 00:11:15.599
butterfly? It's something that you've

00:11:13.760 --> 00:11:17.839
never seen before. What's about to

00:11:15.600 --> 00:11:20.079
happen with the church is

00:11:17.839 --> 00:11:22.320
something that you've never

00:11:20.079 --> 00:11:25.680
experienced before. It's colors on a

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:29.680
mosaic you've never seen, a beautiful

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:32.959
tapestry, a beautiful canvas of the Holy

00:11:29.680 --> 00:11:35.599
Spirit is about to be expressed in a way

00:11:32.959 --> 00:11:39.119
that the world has never seen before."Because

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:42.399
it's His goodness and His mercy.

00:11:39.120 --> 00:11:43.920
As we say, "Show us Your glory,

00:11:42.399 --> 00:11:46.560
Lord.

00:11:43.920 --> 00:11:49.120
Give us an impartation of new

00:11:46.560 --> 00:11:51.199
demonstrations and manifestations of the

00:11:49.120 --> 00:11:54.800
glory that we've never seen before."I

00:11:51.200 --> 00:11:56.880
saw a blowing of goodness and mercy

00:11:54.800 --> 00:12:00.000
coming out of the Father's hand, and He

00:11:56.880 --> 00:12:02.640
blew on it and said it was just

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:04.880
like Moses, Brandon. He said, "Show me

